        { "Header", "Bow" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The recent nerf to the Bow was too harsh\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Charge duration decreased from 2.3s \226\134\146 1.8s" },
        { "Header", "Flamethrower" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Flamethrower was too difficult to counter for how easy it was to play\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Move Speed decreased from Normal \226\134\146 -5%" },
        { "Header", "Shotgun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The recent Shotgun rework unintentionally nerfed it\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage Dropoff start range increased from 0studs \226\134\146 10studs" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage Dropoff end damage increased from 18.75 \226\134\146 25" },
        { "Header", "Energy Pistol" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Energy Pistol\'s high mobility was frustrating to play against\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Movement speed +5% \226\134\146 Normal" },
        { "Header", "Handgun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The recent input-queuing changes made the Handgun much stronger than expected\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 13 \226\134\146 12" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Equip cooldown increased from 0.13s \226\134\146 0.2s" },
        { "Header", "Revolver" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Revolver\'s slower equip speed made it hard to justify picking\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage Dropoff start range increased from 50studs \226\134\146 75studs" },
        { "Header", "Shorty" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Shorty was too reliant on the Freeze Ray\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage Dropoff start range increased from 0studs \226\134\146 7.5studs" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage Dropoff end damage increased from 18.75 \226\134\146 25" },
        { "Header", "Uzi" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Uzi lacked viability in the current meta\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Shoot Cooldown decreased from 0.075s \226\134\146 0.07s" },
        { "Header", "Medkit" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Full healing with the Medkit is too easy to pull off\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Full heal duration increased from 5s \226\134\146 6s" },
        { "Header", "War Horn" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The War Horn ends rounds way too quickly\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Speed Boost decreased from +35% \226\134\146 30%" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Speed Duration increased from 5s \226\134\146 6s" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\155\160 OTHER" },
        { "Description", "Shooting Range dummies have been recolored to red. The DPS dummies are now randomly yellow / purple" },
        { "Description", "You can now equip the same emote multiple times in your emote wheel" },
        { "Description", "The weapon indicator on cosmetic and reward slots is now less intrusive" },
        { "Description", "The Free Rewards page has been refreshed" },
        { "Description", "Improved Prime Weapon UI visuals" },
        { "Description", "New Mythical rarity color" },
        { "Description", "High ELO ranked players can now see a countdown for when their ELO will begin to decay in the Ranked page" },
        { "Description", "Slightly changed the wrap groups on the Hyper Sniper skin for Sniper" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\144\155 BUG FIXES" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where you could see enemies behind a wall for a brief moment after you stop emoting" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where emotes sometimes wouldn\'t stop playing music" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where sometimes players couldn\'t respawn in Arcade Servers" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug where players with lower sensitivities would experience higher viewmodel sway" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug with the Peppergun skin when you reload shortly after equipping" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where the Desert Eagle skin could equip faster than other skins" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where the Void Pistols skin equipped slower than other skins" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where the Hide HUD keybind would activate while typing in the chat window" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where Satchels wouldn\'t stick onto Riot Shields" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug where players would flash red after shooting themselves with splash weapons" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where players couldn\'t respawn in the Hardcore Parkour gamemode" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where the Katana deflect particles would disappear while emoting" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where Elixir would cancel the Medkit healing animation" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where equipping the Riot Shield in your off hand in Double Trouble wouldn\'t block any damage" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug where Riot Shields wouldn\'t be placed on your back properly when unequipped" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where players wouldn\'t be teleported into a rematch if they were in the Shooting Range" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug that caused players not to spawn in at the start of rounds" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug that caused some players to incorrectly show up as Archnemesis in the Duel History page" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug with the traffic cones in the Docks map" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where players were able to teleport out of a matchmade duel during the countdown screen" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where you would get stuck under the ramps in the Splash and Big Splash maps" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug where players could purchase shop items they already own" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\147\156 A NOTE FROM THE DEVELOPERS" },
        { "Description", "We have nothing new to say really besides addressing the new weapons maybe? We would like to iterate that we will NEVER make limited-time weapons, the closest we\'ll get is early-access-style weapons like what we did last year during the holidays and what we\'re doing now with the Season Pass." },
        { "Description", "We would also like to state that Contraband weapons are not meant to be crazy overpowered weapons that dominate every match, we just want them to be extremely unique weapons that stand out way more than Prime weapons. With that being said, we\'ll keep an eye on these new weapons and balance accordingly." },
        { "Description", "Phew, big update! Thank you all for taking the time to check it out! Please welcome our newest full-time developer @GreatGuyBoom, big shoutout to him for helping make this update possible!" }
